 That was what the soldiers did.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 25}Meanwhile near the cross of Jesus were standing his mother and his mother\uc1\u8217*s sister, as well as Mary the wife of Clopas and Mary of Magdala.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 26}When Jesus saw his mother, and the disciple whom he loved, standing near, he said to his mother, \uc1\u8216*There is your son.\uc1\u8217*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 27}Then he said to that disciple, \uc1\u8216*There is your mother.\uc1\u8217* And from that very hour the disciple took her to live in his house.
