{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\cf1\f1\fs22 21}Later on, Jesus showed himself again to the disciples by the Sea of Tiberias.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}It was in this way, \uc1\u8211* Simon Peter, Thomas, who was called \uc1\u8220*The Twin,\uc1\u8221* Nathanael of Cana in Galilee, Zebedee\uc1\u8217*s sons, and two other disciples of Jesus, were together, when Simon Peter said,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}\uc1\u8216*I am going fishing.\uc1\u8217*
