 \uc1\u8216*Tend my sheep,\uc1\u8217* said Jesus.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}The third time, Jesus said to him, \uc1\u8216*Simon, son of John, are you my friend?\uc1\u8217* Peter was hurt at his third question being \uc1\u8220*Are you my friend?\uc1\u8221*; and exclaimed, \uc1\u8216*Master, you know everything! You can tell that I am your friend.\uc1\u8217*
