{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}\uc1\u8216*If it is my will that he should wait until I come,\uc1\u8217* answered Jesus, \uc1\u8216*what has that to do with you? Follow me yourself.\uc1\u8217*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}So the report spread among his followers that that disciple was not to die; yet Jesus did not say that he was not to die, but said \uc1\u8216*If it is my will that he should wait until I come, what has that to do with you?\uc1\u8217*
